-- Alecora Tax & Legal Services - Main office in Marbella, serving expats across Spain
('Alecora Tax & Legal Services', 'Tax/Accounting', 'Chartered accountants and tax advisors specializing in services for English-speaking expats across Spain. With over 15 years of experience and more than 300 companies and individuals served, Alecora provides comprehensive accounting, tax advisory, and legal services. All staff members speak fluent English, ensuring clear communication throughout all procedures. Core services include accounting and bookkeeping for freelancers and companies, Spanish income tax returns (IRPF), non-resident tax returns, company formation and setup, inheritance tax planning, and legal advisory. The team consists of qualified experts in Spanish tax law who help clients minimize tax liabilities while remaining fully compliant. First consultation is free. Services available throughout Spain with primary office on the Costa del Sol.', 'C/Virgen del Pilar nº 4, Edificio España, Planta 1, Puerta 1, 29601 Marbella', 'Marbella', 'Málaga', '+34 625 457 816', 'info@alecora.com', 'https://accountantsspain.com/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW()),

